resources.string:
Quran Android is a free, open source Quran application for Android. The images used are from the quran.com project, and the data used in the translations and Arabic comes from tanzil.net. 

Credits: 
 @fo2ad - audio recitation support 
 @wnafee - page flip animation (based on android-page-curl project) 
 @hams_rrr - arabic support for non-arabic phones 
 @neo_4583 - arabic reshaper project 
 @somaiagabr - graphics and arabic translation 
 Mehmed Mahmudoglu - turkish translation 

New features in this release: 
- Audio Recitations (thanks to @fo2ad) 
- Minor bugfixes. 

La tansawna men saleh el doaa.
